 and geographies” said jackie rantanen principal in the product management group at hamilton lane hamilton lane has been managing fundsoffunds strategies since  and seeks to provide access to the top echelon of funds worldwide through its robust platform leveraging the firm’s global presence and rigorous due diligence process the fund represents a continuation of hamilton lane’s tailored fundsoffunds approach to provide investors with a balanced portfolio of private market investments about hamilton lane hamilton lane is an independent alternative investment management firm providing innovative private markets solutions to sophisticated investors around the world the firm has been dedicated to private markets investing for more than two decades and currently has more than  employees operating in offices throughout the us london hong kong rio de janeiro tel aviv and tokyo with over  billion in total assets under management and supervision hamilton lane offers a full range of investment products and services that enable clients to participate in the private markets asset class on a global and customized basis the firm has been named an inc  fastestgrowing company and a “best places to work in money management by pensions  investments for more information please visit wwwhamiltonlanecom  as of december   contact kate dillon prosek partners   ext  kdillonprosekcom  principles for responsible investment  integrating esg in private equity « previous  hamilton lane recognized as top global company for the professional advancement of women next »   philadelphialondonmunichsydneyhong kongrio de janeirosan franciscosan diegonew yorkmiamitel avivtokyolas vegasseoul home              terms of use              site index copyright   hamilton lane all rights reserved hamilton lane incorporated private company information  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of hamilton lane incorporated snapshot people company overview hamilton lane incorporated is an investm